/// Per-row RMS norm: `y[i, :] = x[i, :] / sqrt(mean(x[i, :]^2) + eps)`.
/// Pure Rust so it is identical for both backends; the parity test
/// is about MLX vs CPU on shared scaffolding, not about RMS norm
